To run the tool please download entire repository
Create a file on your flashdrive called "setup" 
Unzip repository into the setup folder you just created

On the new PC ->
Connect to mozilla guest
run "firefox configuration.bat" 
Accept the prompt or hit yes
enter in the computer name
hit enter
walk away for about 6 minutes
come back and enter the recovery password for bitlocker into WDE
hit enter
Done
